Sacyr Seeks Lenders to Refinance Repsol Loan in Chile, Confidencial Says

-- B y   E s t e b a n   D u a r t e
-- 
2011-10-12T06:21:48Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-12/sacyr-seeks-banks-for-repsol-loan-in-chile-confidencial-says.html
Sacyr Vallehermoso SA (SYV) ’s Chairman
Luis del Rivero is visiting banks in Chile as the builder seeks
a lender to refinance a loan used to buy a 20 percent stake in
 Repsol YPF SA (REP) ,  El Confidencial  reported, without citing anyone.  The Spanish builder’s executives also plan to invite
lenders from Brazil, Canada, China,  South Africa  and Australia
to join the transaction, the newspaper said. Sacyr is seeking
new lenders as some of the group of existing banks may be not
be willing to refinance the loan, according to El Confidencial.  To contact the reporters on this story:
Esteban Duarte in Madrid at 
 eduarterubia@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Emma Ross-Thomas at 
 erossthomas@bloomberg.net  